      "category": "team",
      "content": "Proxy-Authorization header not cleared on cross-origin redirect in fetch\n\nImpact\nUndici already cleared Authorization headers on cross-origin redirects, but did not clear Proxy-Authorization headers.\n\nPatches\nThis is patched in v5.28.3 and v6.6.1\n\nWorkarounds\nThere are no known workarounds.\n\nFull GHSA: https://github.com/nodejs/undici/security/advisories/GHSA-3787-6prv-h9w3",
